caption.text:
Thought I'd finally delve into the Storybook series of the modern Sonic era.  Even as a huge Sonic fan, I was very apprehensive about these titles because they were more motion sensor focused (not a huge fan of that kind of gimmick). I tried Secret Rings at a Gamestop a million years ago and wasn't super impressed by the waggly/on-track gameplay style.  Since their release the internet came crashing down on these two, which also sullied my opinion of them.  However, I can't call myself a Sonic fan if I don't, at least, give them a try.  Just to see it for myself (it also didn't hurt that they were only $2.99 each at my local game store 😁😁🤫).

Немного развернутой информации о том, как ведет себя игровой искусственный интеллект в The Last of Us: Part II

Если вы бесшумно убили врага с помощью лука или пистолета с прикрепленным глушителем, то его напарник все еще может найти тело, затем он посмотрит, где находится стрела или пуля в трупе, и после этого сделает вывод, в каком направлении был атакован его товарищ. Но при этом он не будет знать вашего точного местоположения, а погрузится в рассуждение

Даже если игрок способен постоянно выходить из ситуации и вечно опережать своих врагов, то и в этом случае нужно быть аккуратным, бой в любом случае не будет легким

caption.text:
3 people more than 15 hours and still counting, collisions only work in x axis in the first row.

programing in assembly is super hard but we have been working today for 10 and we didn't want to go home, we are crying inside, not because we are tired, but  because we want to finish it, WE ARE HAVING FUN!

for those who like programing, seriously start learning assembly it won't be useful for having a game done but you will enjoy it, and it will make you a better programmer. ------------\(^o^)/-------------- #videogames #gaming #gamedev #videogamedev #indiegamedev  #gamedevelopment #videogamedevelopment #indiegamedevelopment #retrogamedev #retrogamedevelopment #cpcretrodev #cpcretrodev2019 #cpcretrodev19 #amstradcpc #z80 #assemblycode #assembly #ua #universidaddealicante #students #stratup #gamestudio #games

caption.text:
*SPOILER WARNING*
-
Alright so, I beat Astral Chain, about 3 days ago. And ooohhh my gawd lemme tell you. This game, is bombastic. I give it an 11/10. Worth every cent tbh. The cutscenes were cool, fighting didn't get stale, it is kinda like Bayonetta's combat style, but with way more options. The story was kinda obvious tbh, but everything else made up for it. Customization was pretty cool, it has lots of content and missions to complete. Selfie mode was cool asf. Voice acting was nice, and just ugh, it was so perfect to me. Watch the clips I uploaded by swiping right (if you don't mind spoilers) 😍 THE MUSIC DUDE. UGH I LOVED IT. I'VE LISTENED TO IT ON YOUTUBE SO MANY TIMES LMAO. But yeah, I highly recommend you check this game out. 💕
-

caption.text:
Game of the day, Internationalsoccer for the Atari 2600.  Released in 1982 by M Network(Mattel Electronics), it is for 2 players and follows soccer rules.  Each player has to score more goals then the other in two 45 minute periods(simulated time). Each player controls one player in the field at a time while the computer controls the rest.  The player can dribble and pass, and features throw ins, corner kicks, goal kicks, and over time in the event of a tie.  There are also several.skill levels which affect the speed of the game.

Hi Gamers,
Let’s head back, just a little bit..Okay to be honest, 11 years ago, to 2008.

In October 2008, Ubisoft released Far Cry 2. An open world first-person shooter, that takes place in a modern-day Central African nation during civil war. You, the player,takes control of a mercenary on a lengthy journey to locate and assassinate "The Jackal", a notorious arms dealer.

The game was met with positive reception upon release with critics praising the game's open-ended gameplay, the AI, the settings and the visuals of the game. Some reports state that the game was ahead of it’s time.

Some interesting facts about the game, is that you as a player, yell in Afrikaans if you are caught in a gunfight, you have to take your Malaria Pills otherwise you will die, you carry syrettes with you to aid yourself if you loose health and when nearing death(when only one health bar remains) you, the player, have to perform first-aid to your character, for example removing bullets with pliers or snapping or twisting broken fingers back into place.

The game has realistic features such as weapon degradation and the dynamic weather system. The player needs to hold a physical map and use a handheld navigation system (which highly resembles a military-type GPS) to get around, but they are automatically updated as the player travels through the environment.

For me, a gamer that never got into the Far Cry Franchise, Far Cry 2 is a definitely must play and just to enjoy a game that has made his mark silently into our hearts. The game is Backwards compataible with Xbox one.
So if you are a Xbox gamer, get it, play it and enjoy it.

Leave a comment about this game or any other game you think is underrated and needs more appreciation.💪🎮 - Gommie😎

أكثر الشركات التي تدور حولها الشائعات، Rockstar Games وماهو مشروعهم القادم، هل هو Grand Theft Auto 6 أو Bully 2؟
-
اخر الشائعات التي ظهرت على الإنترنت وبالتحديد موقع Reddit ذكرت بأن Grand Theft Auto 6 هي بالفعل تحت التطوير الكامل منذ ٢٠١٨ تحت الاسم الرمزي Project Americas، كما أشيع مسبقاً.
-
الاستوديو الذي يتولى تطويرها هو Rockstar North، بينما Rockstar India مسؤولون حالياً عن Bully 2 للجيل الحالي والقادم.
-
اللعبة تدور أحداثها في Vice City، والخريطة ستضم مدن ومستنقعات وجزر صغيرة وكبيرة، وستكون أفضل من Grand Theft Auto 5. كما سيكون هناك مهمات محددة في Liberty City
-
أسلوب اللعب سيكون شبيه بالجزء الخامس، لكن هناك اختلافات ستجعله مميز. تدور أحداث اللعبة في عدة فترات زمنية مختلفة واللاعب سيرى التغير الذي سيطرأ على المدينة والمركبات مع التقدم في القصة.
-
الطقس والتقلبات الجوية وتنوعها سيلعب دوراً كبيراً في هذا الجزء، لذلك توقع وجود صواعق، فيضانات، وأعاصير.
-
تماماً كالجزء الخامس، قرارتك واختياراتك هي التي ستحدد نهاية القصة.
-
كل هذي إشاعة، لكن شي جميل ودي يكون حقيقة، انتوا وش رايكم؟ 😍

caption.text:
Okay so my selfie game may not be strong here so please forgive me 😝 but I feel good today and I wanted to show off my new Mario Kart sweater that I just got. I know I’m going to wear this one into the ground. At the store they only had this one size and when it fit perfectly it’s like it was waiting there all along for me. Most days on my day off I tend to stay at home like a bit of a recluse and try to get a bunch of things done. Today I decided to take myself out for amazing drive with the top down, music playing and I visited one of my favourite beaches out of town that reminds me of my adventures in Hawaii 🌸 . Sometimes you just gotta ignore the chores and endless to-do lists and enjoy life and all the magical moments and take time for yourself. It’s something I have to try to remember. Hope your all having a great day and that you found time to do something for yourself today, if you did what was it? ❤️. It’s okay if it’s even finding time to play your favourite game, that’s what I plan to do later 😝. The sweater gives you a good indication of what I will play.
.
.
.

caption.text: Sometimes you just have to take a day and focus on your hobby. I love gunpla and model kits. I took the diamond loot chest Sanctuary 3 model and did a full repaint on the shell. Took it from a bland tan/grey to a high polish brushed silver. Then I went in an weathered the whole ship slightly, to provide accents. I painted all the windows and the bridge French blue for a better pop, and detailed the mechanical elements with red along with finally adding the decals. The paint job is done but next day off I’m going to add blue LEDs to all the engines to provide a wicked visual effect. #costume #cosplay #hobby #modelkits #borderlands #borderlands3 #sanctuary3 #prop #repaint #ps4 #xbox1 #pcmasterrace #videogames #hobbiest

caption.text:
💬 Deixe seu comentário, adoramos ouvir você!

Eita, que bagunça! Confundimos a cabeça de vocês, não foi? Calma crianças, nós explicamos! 🖒
O que acontece é que na versão japonesa os lutadores abaixo que estão na esquerda tem seus nomes trocados pelos que estão na direita.

Balrog = M. Bison
Vega = Balrog
M. Bison = Vega

Esperamos ter esclarecido tudo agora! Interessante essa curiosidade... 🤔

Я и море.
Когда впервые встречаешь его такое тихое и спокойное, и в спокойствие своём величественное ..всегда я чувствую себя дома с ним, я дышу вместе с приливами и отливами, также гармонично..как и волны. Как в колыбели тебя баюкает мама.
Когда море волнуется, сразу ощущаешь хрупкость мира,как,в каждую секунду где-то происходит исход и что-то неизбежное ..
И никогда не изведать его глубины, оно скрывает столько тайн и манит и манит...
И раскрывает нас самих. От моря пахнёт одиночеством.
И в конце пути человек остаётся один на один с собой и со своими мыслями , которые как волны накатывают порой превращаясь в цунами, руша все или наоборот затихая в штиль.
Старик и море 🌊 Хемингуэй. Я люблю эту книгу за чувства, переданные в ней.

caption.text:
.
Today’s Game: Dragon Quest XI S - Echoes of an Elusive Age
Platform: Nintendo Switch
——-
I beat Dragon Quest Builders 2 late Saturday night, I’m sorry to see it be finished, but I’ll return to it one day. Today I started on Dragon Quest XI S, and I’m loving the skillful mix of drama, humor, and story development. I love Sylvando, he is my favorite character so far. I love hearing him talk, and I know for certain that if he were real he would treat me right. I feel like I’ve advanced very far very soon, so I think I need to slow it down and explore more, fight more, because the story feels like it’s zipping along.
——-
🎮🕹🐲⚔️🛡🧙‍♀️👧🤡🕹🎮
——-
